title: “Welcome to the Panderdome.” (LIVE from Des Moines)
description: Trump caves on his Mexican trade war, and the race to win Iowa brings 19 Democratic candidates to Cedar Rapids. Des Moines Register pollster Ann Selzer joins Jon, Jon, Tommy, Dan, and Connie Schultz on stage in Des Moines, Iowa.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
